{"tid":415743,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[跪地求些牙]小弟同個FD整左隻關於香港同選舉既BOARD GAME...","createTime":"2017-09-27T08:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T09:17:13.000Z","uid":150512,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1708b8ed51c0df246a38167cccd69b44db0ed9bb","tid":415743,"uid":150512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T08:47:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n小弟呢半年同個FD整左隻BOARD GAME係關於香港同埋選舉既放左上KICKSTARTER度眾籌~希望咁多位巴絲唔BACK都望兩眼 能夠幫手些牙既小弟真係跪地伏拜  <br />\n<br />\n[有圖有真相] <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/164537_d5602f7cfd23763a6d2d44030c3f3deb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F164537_d5602f7cfd23763a6d2d44030c3f3deb.png&h=eaf8438a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻GAME個中文名就叫「選舉工程」，顧名思義，就係比咁多位巴絲試下做政黨去打贏一場選戰。  <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/164551_6753c42d66cbad62b642d025ddb28bf6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F164551_6753c42d66cbad62b642d025ddb28bf6.png&h=d38edb5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁要隻GAME度贏就有好多野可以做既，你可以係張香港地圖上面行黎行去去攞支持，唔知有咩既又可以睇下D目標卡睇下有咩野可以做。  <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/164601_01508d7de2470e6247e70c75a9d2f765.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F164601_01508d7de2470e6247e70c75a9d2f765.png&h=226584cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玩埋事件卡既話隻GAME就更多變化喇~  <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/164629_61def5135e8a4423e33c977fc20ab1ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F164629_61def5135e8a4423e33c977fc20ab1ef.jpg&h=d892d3b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/164636_fb91273e9bd66c870ddb1d19771edb98.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F164636_fb91273e9bd66c870ddb1d19771edb98.png&h=1dde7cfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁多位巴絲有興趣想知點玩既話可以上以下呢個網會有更多簡介 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongnightdreamer.com/electioneer-c \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongnightdreamer.com%2Felectioneer-c%20&d=1Bsysqd9aMMxOoQO0Q2moJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=011b4091\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongnightdreamer.com/electioneer-c </a> <br />\n咁當然有興趣支持我地隻GAME就更加歡迎啦~LINK係下面呢條 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/hongkongnightdreamer/electioneer?ref=dm6arh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Fhongkongnightdreamer%2Felectioneer%3Fref%3Ddm6arh&d=1Bsysqd9aMMxOoQO0Q2moJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=e3abdee4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/hongkongnightdreamer/electioneer?ref=dm6arh</a> <br />\n希望咁多位大大比下面~"},{"pid":"8ed687a862b999eb71cffd1788c40c20498c5866","tid":415743,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b4e6e06c8220d4932c296edce7c6e51b9b3950","tid":415743,"uid":140776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T08:53:55.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"85c23b187e40ec7b0aa914513492c2e7d0cfafd2","tid":415743,"uid":44461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:02:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d3238c8b433665a5998d3680064bd689715bf55a","tid":415743,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:13:34.000Z","msg":"有d 似世界首腦會議"},{"pid":"b2f0eafdcdbd50a3a0404d05c997e852fcb97dcd","tid":415743,"uid":150512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:17:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有d 似世界首腦會議</blockquote><br />\nChing唔同架唔同架"}]}